name: A Few Holes and One Chipmunk
name_original: A Few Holes and One Chipmunk
description:
Created by high_sc0re and Pixelat3dGamer for the Brackeys' 2020 GameJam (first game jam for both of us! It was a great time.)

You control a chipmunk with  chaotic powers.

Have fun in the infinite hole.

Cupcake.
